/ Projects (projects/index)

%h1.page-header Projects

/ filter by category?
.row.project-types
  %h3 Web Development
  %h3 Graphic Design

%hr.line

/ Listing Web Development Projects
.project-row-header
  %h2 Web Development
- @projects_webdevelopment.each_with_index do |project, i|
  .row.project-item
    = link_to project.url do
      = image_tag project.image_url, size: "700x400", :class => "img-responsive"
    %h3= link_to project.title, project

%hr.line

